## XState Viewport Machine

This POC demonstrates the viewport state machine for the MMS Fractal Canvas.

### States
- **idle**: Ready for user input
- **panning**: User is dragging to pan
- **pinching**: User is pinch-zooming (touch)
- **momentum**: Inertial panning after release
- **animating**: Smooth transition to target position/zoom

### LOD Levels
- **Strategic** (zoom < 0.3x): 10-12 year heatmap view
- **Tactical** (0.3x - 1.0x): 1-3 year workload bars
- **Operational** (1.0x - 3.0x): 1-6 month Gantt view
- **Execution** (> 3.0x): 1-4 week detailed tasks

### Interactions
- **Scroll**: Zoom in/out centered on cursor
- **Drag**: Pan the viewport
- **Double-click**: Zoom 2x at click position
- **Buttons**: Zoom controls, reset, jump to today
        `,
      },
    },
  },
};

export default meta;
